              <span id="reviewTextContainer1428532643" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10142747033011286346">This book was a story that gripped my heart each page I read. The unending love that Hadriel has for his childhood sweetheart is something that all people have experienced. The puppy love is wonderful to experience and this book allowed me to re-experience that again through Hadriel. The story takes us from South America to the USA and keeps us engaged every word on the way. Mr. Alexander has proven that the end of our life is still an opportunity for us to revisit and explore the world still. T</span>
  <span id="freeText10142747033011286346" style="display:none">This book was a story that gripped my heart each page I read. The unending love that Hadriel has for his childhood sweetheart is something that all people have experienced. The puppy love is wonderful to experience and this book allowed me to re-experience that again through Hadriel. The story takes us from South America to the USA and keeps us engaged every word on the way. Mr. Alexander has proven that the end of our life is still an opportunity for us to revisit and explore the world still. This book is very detailed in that it creates a movie in your head with every place we go in the book. If you want to think about your happier days, or feel up to finding out what real love looks like, then this is your book. It is a book that can be finished in a weekend, because you find yourself desperate to see Hadriel find the happiness he's always sought.</span>
